Senior Cost Accounting - PT Formulatrix Indonesia
Senior Cost Accounting  -
Senior Cost Accounting
Responsibilities
Responsibilities: Data Collection• Mapping / construct data accumulatrion systems for cost accounting system• Create and review the controls needed for data accumulatrion and reporting systems by products Inventory• Coordinate physical inventory counts and cycle counts every day by products category• Investigate cycle counting variances and resolve issues• Update standard costs in BOM• Verify and validate the COGS (Direct labor, Materials and FOH components) as part of the month-end close Analysis• To compare and analyze periodically the variances and their causes between standard cost and actual cost• Analyze the FOH components monthly  General Requirements:Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent.Required skill(s): erp system, cost accounting, analyst cost accounting, Accounting system.Required language(s): EnglishAt least 4 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Applicants must be willing to work in Jl. Soekarno Hatta 121 Salatiga.Preferably Supervisor / Coordinators specializing in Finance - General/Cost Accounting or equivalent.Full-Time position(s) available.
